---
title: Hake in Lemon Mustard Sauce		 with sweet potato fries and pan-fried broccoli
description: Hake is a fish that's delicate in texture and mild in taste. This means it pairs particularly well with strong and vibrant flavours like the mustard, lemon, and honey that make up the sumptuous sauce in this dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R05_W05_IE_IEFF13182-2_KB_Main_high-83402d72.jpg
